Tagging is a unique and innovative way of adding your product at the Paytm Marketplace. It saves a lot of time for the you as a seller in terms of uploading your catalogue.
<h3>How you ask?</h3>
Let's say you want to sell a pen drive called XYZ. This product may often be listed with another seller as well. So all you need to do is tag your product - XYZ to the existing listing of the product on the Paytm Marketplace and start selling instantly.

